# wizcli

Control your WiZ light from the terminal.

```bash
# turn on
$ wiz on

# turn off
$ wiz off

# dim to 20%
$ wiz dim 20

# set temp to 50%
$ wiz temp 50

# set cold
$ wiz cold

# set hot
$ wiz hot

# set RGB color
$ wiz rgb 255 40 90
```

